Download the Pip script
Go to the following site:
https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py
Right click and save txt as a file.
Remember this file location.

Install pip in Python (Windows 10)
Open [Windows] Command Prompt (Not Python's)
Navigate to the location of the file in the previous step.
type the following command:
python get-pip.py

Alternatively, you can open it with python and run the F5 to run the script

Install Netmiko in python (Windows 10)
Open [Windows] Command Prompt (Not Python's)
type the following command:
python -m pip install netmiko
